metadata.name: Can You See Me?
metadata.description:
ANZART's Open Edition: Can you see me? 

Out in the woods? 
Invisible, forgotten  
A ghost in the shadows  
My brush brings color to my world  
But to others, I am a blur

But I persist, I create  
For the love of the craft  
Hoping someday, someone  
Will see me, will recognize  
My talent, my worth

Until then, 
I remain content in my solitude.  
For I am, the invisible artist.

This is a tribute to everyone hidden in the shadows.
